-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESonakshi%20Pandey%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20a%20cloud%20computing%20product%20manager%20at%20Google%20in%20Seattle.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20employment%20history.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20three%20years%20into%20my%20career%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20when%20I%20realized%20I%20wanted%20to%20challenge%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20coding%20but%20was%20keen%20on%20a%20role%20that%20was%20less%20desk-bound%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20meet%20people%20and%20speak%20in%20public%2C%20something%20that%20made%20me%20anxious%20because%20I%20have%20always%20been%20an%20introvert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20a%20solution%20architecture%20role%20would%20be%20a%20good%20entry%20point%2C%20and%20I%20interviewed%20to%20move%20to%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20from%20Amazon.com%2C%20where%20I%20was%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20role%20and%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20speak%20at%20client%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20first%20few%20presentations%20were%20very%20rocky%3A%20I%20struggled%20with%20confidence%2C%20imposter%20syndrome%2C%20and%20memorizing%20a%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20hours%20of%20practice%20presentations%20and%20guidance%20from%20various%20mentors%20to%20help%20me%20become%20a%20person%20who%20speaks%20comfortably%20at%20meetings%20and%20tech%20conferences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20selective%20about%20who%20I%20choose%20to%20mentor.%20Here's%20why%20I%20do%20it%20and%20how%20I%20pick%20mentees%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec67a0eb-f1c0-4f39-b0d5-01c675268c90%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBeing%20a%20mentor%20benefits%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mentor%20interns%20at%20Google%20and%20a%20variety%20of%20people%20at%20various%20stages%20of%20their%20careers%20who%20reach%20out%20on%20LinkedIn%20or%20other%20social%20media.%20I%20am%20al