0guess%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20you%20are%20most%20excited%20about%20your%20marriage%20and%20the%20children%20you%20will%20bring%20into%20this%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButker%20then%20mentioned%20his%20wife%2C%20whom%20he%20said%20embraced%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20important%20titles%20of%20all%3A%20homemaker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20say%20all%20of%20this%20to%20you%20because%20I%20have%20seen%20it%20firsthand%20how%20much%20happier%20someone%20can%20be%20when%20they%20disregard%20the%20outside%20noise%20and%20move%20closer%20and%20closer%20to%20God's%20will%20in%20their%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b831c62e-116e-48f5-82f0-2c132ee8f0b2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%20shouldn't%20be%20shamed%20for%20the%20path%20they%20choose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EButker's%20comments%20sparked%20online%20debates%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharrison-butker-speech-mom-physicist-chiefs-homemaker-masculinity-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20in%20the%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.betterwithphoebe.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhoebe%20Gavin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20career%20and%20leadership%20coach%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20women%20should%20have%20the%20space%20and%20opportunity%20to%20determine%20their%20future%20based%20on%20their%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20pro-women%20having%20choices%20and%20women%20being%20able%20to%20make%20those%20choices%20based%20on%20what%20intrinsically%20motivates%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavin%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20women%20who%20are%20going%20to%20choose%20to%20embrace%20motherhood%20as%20a%20primary%20motivation%20in%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20then%20there%20are%20women%20who%20are%20going%20to%20make%20other%20choices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGavin%20added%20some%20women%20want%20both%20a%20career%20and%20motherhood%2C%20while%20others%20want%20neither.%20None%20of%20these%20choices%20should%20be%20ridiculed%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20people%20who%20truly%20believe%20that%20is%20the%20right%20decision%20for%20them%2C%20and%20if%20that's%20what%20they%20believe%2C%20then%20I%20fully%20embrace%2C%20empower%2C%20and%20encourage%20them%20to%20go%20down%20that%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20issue%20is%20pushing%20those%20sorts%20of%20values%20upon%20other%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20she%20takes%20issue%20with%20Benedictine%20College's%20decision%20to%20choose%20Butker%20as%20a%20commencement%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Benedictine%20College%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e31bcfe5bc79c4b3958e2d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBenedictine%20College.%20%3Cp%3EBenedictine%20College%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20should%20have%20known%20that%20he%20was%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20that%20they%20would%20want%20to%20put%20in%20front%20of%20these%20grads%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bchallenging%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20young%20female%20graduates%20who%20had%20spent%20at%20least%20four%20years%20working%20toward%20professional%20careers%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20told%20that%20they're%20doing%20the%20wrong%20thing%20and%20that%20they%20should%20be%20doing%20something%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJessica%20Schaefer%2C%20a%20crisis%20communications%20and%20reputation%20management%20expert%2C%20echoed%20Gavin's%20thoughts.%20She%20said%20commencement%20speeches%20are%20meant%20to%20be%20inspiring%2C%20not%20a%20platform%20to%20share%20personal%20opinions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20someone%20who%20works%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20commencement%20speeches%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20you%20prepare.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20inspire%20everyone%20that's%20graduating%2C%26quot%3B%20Schaefer%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20a%20platform%20for%20your%20personal%20opinion.%20That's%20not%20why%20you're%20getting%20paid%20to%20give%20a%20commencement%20speech.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGavin%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bwhatever%20choice%20a%20woman%20makes%2C%20they%20should%20be%20able%20to%20make%20that%20choice%20and%20live%20without%20shame.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20giving%20his%20speech%2C%20several%20people%20have%20spoken%20out%20against%20Butker%20and%20Benedictine%20College.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Football%20League%20distanced%20itself%20from%20Butker%20with%20a%20statement%20praising%20inclusivity.%20Teammates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravis-kelce-reacts-harrison-butker-catholic-commencement-speech-taylor-swift-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETravis%20Kelce%20and%20Patrick%20Mahomes%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20they%20disagreed%20with%20Butker's%20comments%20but%20defended%20his%20right%20to%20voice%20his%20opinion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcatholic-nuns-rebuke-harrison-butker-commencement-speech-benedictine-college-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enuns%20from%20Benedictine%20College%3C%2Fa%3E%20denounced%20Butker's%20speech%2C%20saying%20they%20disagreed%20with%20the%20suggestion%20that%20%26quot%3Bbeing%20a%20homemaker%20is%20the%20highest%20calling%26quot%3B%20for%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20sisters%20have%20dedicated%20our%20lives%20to%20God%20and%20God's%20people%2C%20including%20the%20many%20women%20whom%20we%20have%20taught%20and%20influenced%20during%20the%20past%20160%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%20%26quot%3BThese%20women%20have%20made%20a%20tremendous%20difference%20in%20the%20world%20in%20their%20roles%20as%20wives%20and%20mothers%20and%20through%20their%20God-given%20gifts%