he%20coasts%20of%20Bangladesh%20and%20adjoining%20West%20Bengal%2C%20bringing%20heavy%20rains%20that%20flooded%20homes%20and%20farmland%2C%20and%20leaving%20a%20trail%20of%20destruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landfall%20process%20began%20at%208%3A30%20pm%20on%20Sunday%20over%20the%20adjacent%20coasts%20of%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Bangladesh%20between%20Sagar%20Island%20and%20Khepupara%2C%20near%20the%20southwest%20of%20Mongla%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'Remal'%20flattened%20fragile%20dwellings%2C%20uprooted%20trees%20and%20knocked%20down%20electric%20poles.%20One%20person%20was%20injured%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20debris%20in%20the%20Gosaba%20area%20of%20the%20Sundarbans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20one%20lakh%20people%20were%20evacuated%20from%20vulnerable%20areas%20in%20West%20Bengal%20before%20the%20cyclone%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSevere%20cyclonic%20storm%20Remal%20made%20landfall%20between%20Sagar%20Island%20in%20West%20Bengal%20and%20Khepupara%20in%20Bangladesh%20on%20Sunday%20night%20with%20wind%20speeds%20reaching%20up%20to%20135%20kmph%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20meteorological%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20footage%20showed%20gigantic%20tidal%20waves%20crashing%20into%20a%20seawall%20in%20coastal%20resort%20town%20of%20Digha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20coastline%20was%20blurred%20by%20thick%20sheets%20of%20rain%20as%20the%20cyclone%20made%20landfall%2C%20with%20surging%20waters%20sweeping%20fishing%20boats%20inland%20and%20inundating%20mud-and-thatch%20houses%20and%20farmlands%20in%20low-lying%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Kolkata's%20Bibir%20Bagan%20area%2C%20one%20person%20was%20injured%20when%20a%20wall%20collapsed%20due%20to%20a%20heavy%20downpour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20from%20North%20and%20South%2024%20Parganas%20and%20East%20Midnapore%20districts%20stated%20roofs%20of%20thatched%20houses%20were%20blown%20away%2C%20electric%20poles%20twisted%20and%20trees%20uprooted%20in%20several%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStreets%20and%20homes%20in%20low-lying%20areas%20adjoining%20Kolkata%20were%20inundated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20government%20shifted%20around%201.10%20lakh%20people%20from%20coastal%20and%20vulnerable%20areas%20to%20cyclone%20shelters%2C%20schools%20and%20colleges%20by%20Sunday%20late%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvacuation%20efforts%20focused%20on%20relocating%20people%20from%20South%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20especially%20Sagar%20Island%2C%20Sundarbans%20and%20Kakdwip%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20to%20review%20the%20response%20and%20preparedness%20for%20the%20storm%2C%20while%20West%20Bengal%20Governor%20Dr%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%20monitored%20the%20situation%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20urged%20people%20to%20stay%20at%20home%20and%20assuring%20them%20of%20her%20government's%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(KMC)%20authorities%20evacuated%20people%20from%20high-rises%20and%20dilapidated%20buildings%2C%20according%20to%20Mayor%20Firhad%20Hakim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHakim%20mentioned%20that%2015%2C000%20civic%20employees%20were%20mobilised%20to%20address%20post-cyclone%20scenarios%2C%20with%20equipment%20ready%20for%20quick%20removal%20of%20large%20uprooted%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cyclone%20caused%20light%20rains%20and%20winds%20in%20areas%20like%20Digha%2C%20Kakdwip%20and%20Jaynagar%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20intensify%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20Meteorological%20Department's%20eastern%20regional%20head%20Somnath%20Dutta%20indicated%20that%20southern%20Bengal%20districts%20would%20experience%20increasing%20winds%20and%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourteen%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(NDRF)%20teams%20were%20deployed%20across%20districts%20in%20south%20Bengal%2C%20including%20Kolkata.%20