ol%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20met%20department%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20forward%20sector%20of%20wall%20cloud%20region%20is%20entering%20into%20land.%20The%20landfall%20process%20has%20commenced%20over%20coastal%20areas%20of%20Bangladesh%20and%20adjoining%20West%20Bengal.%20It%20will%20continue%20for%20next%204%20hours%26quot%3B.%20Wind%20speeds%20are%20expected%20to%20range%20between%20110%20and%20120%20km%20per%20hour%20and%20gusts%20can%20reach%20up%20to%20135%20kmph.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECoastal%20districts%20are%20expected%20to%20experience%20extremely%20heavy%20rainfall%2C%20while%20Kolkata%20and%20its%20surroundings%20may%20encounter%20heavy%20to%20very%20heavy%20rainfall.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20held%20a%20meeting%20earlier%20this%20evening%20to%20check%20the%20preparedness%20for%20Cyclone%20Remal.%20He%20said%20the%20Centre%20has%20extended%20full%20support%20to%20the%20state%20and%20must%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%20More%20teams%20of%20security%20forces%20have%20been%20kept%20on%20standby%2C%20he%20said.Sixteen%20battalions%20each%20from%20the%20state%20disaster%20management%20and%20NDRF%20have%20already%20been%20deployed%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAir%20and%20rail%20traffic%20have%20already%20been%20shut%20ahead%20of%20the%20landfall%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure.%20Kolkata%20airport%20authorities%20have%20suspended%20flight%20operations%20for%2021%20hours%20starting%20at%20noon%20today.%20The%20Eastern%20and%20South%20Eastern%20Railways%20have%20cancelled%20several%20trains.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20total%20of%20394%20flights%20-%20both%20international%20and%20domestic%20-%20will%20not%20operate%20during%20the%20flight%20suspension%20period%2C%20an%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(AAI)%20official%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKolkata%20and%20its%20adjoining%20districts%20have%20been%20receiving%20intermittent%20showers%20and%20gusty%20winds%20since%20morning.%20Traffic%20has%20been%20thin%20on%20the%20roads.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EKolkata%20mayor%20Firhad%20Hakim%20convened%20a%20meeting%20with%20officials%20in%20the%20afternoon%20to%20assess%20preparedness%20for%20the%20impending%20cyclone.%20He%20added%20that%20approximately%2015%2C000%20civic%20employees%20have%20been%20mobilised%20to%20address%20post-cyclone%20scenarios.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Bengal%20government%20has%20evacuated%20around%201.10%20lakh%20people%20from%20coastal%20regions%2C%20including%20the%20Sundarbans%20and%20Sagar%20Island%2C%20to%20secure%20shelters.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAuthorities%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20especially%20in%20Digha%2C%20Shankarpur%2C%20and%20Tajpur%2C%20have%20issued%20advisories%20urging%20tourists%20to%20vacate%20hotels%20and%20refrain%20from%20venturing%20into%20the%20seas%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20Bangladesh%2C%20over%20800%2C000%20people%20from%20vulnerable%20areas%20have%20been%20evacuated%20to%20shelters%20on%20Sunday.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3E(The%20Kolkata%20Police%20has%20also%20announced%20two%20helpline%20numbers%20-%209432610428%20and%209432610429%20-%20for%20citizens)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716748800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F4mt8h1jk_cyclone-remal_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-remal-landfall-pm-modi-holds-meet-to-check-preparations-10-points-5751021%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cyclone%20Remal%20has%20started%20the%20process%20of%20landfall%20between%20Bangladesh%20and%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20process%20is%20expected%20to%20continue%20for%20four%20hours%2C%20the%20meteorological%20department%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fahead-of-remal-landfall-pm-modi-holds-meet-to-check-preparations-10-points-5751021%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%