%2C%26quot%3B%20Clinton%20told%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20that%20Democrats%20believed%20that%20the%20court%20system%20and%20legal%20precedents%20would%20protect%20abortion%20rights%20%E2%80%94%20until%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-abortion-decision-final-ruling-scotus-roe-v-wade-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20those%20rights%20were%20not%20protected%20by%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20take%20it%20seriously%2C%20and%20we%20didn't%20understand%20the%20threat%2C%26quot%3B%20Clinton%2C%20the%20party's%202016%20presidential%20nominee%2C%20told%20the%20Times.%20%26quot%3BMost%20Democrats%2C%20most%20Americans%2C%20did%20not%20realize%20we%20are%20in%20an%20existential%20struggle%20for%20the%20future%20of%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20could%20have%20done%20more%20to%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20book%2C%20written%20by%20Times%20journalists%20Elizabeth%20Dias%20and%20Lisa%20Lerer%2C%20explores%20the%20decadeslong%20push%20to%20dismantle%20Roe%20v.%20Wade%20and%20the%20ramifications%20of%20its%20demise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20Clinton%20lamented%20that%20Democrats%20were%20%26quot%3Btaken%20by%20surprise%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20Dobbs%20decision.%20She%20argued%20that%20she%20never%20became%20complacent%20over%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20conservative-led%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20reverse%20Roe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20I%20give%20the%20right%20credit%20for%20is%20they%20never%20give%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20Times.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20relentless.%20You%20know%2C%20they%20take%20a%20loss.%20They%20get%20back%20up.%20They%20regroup.%20They%20raise%20more%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20tremendously%20impressive%20the%20way%20that%20they%20operate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20contin