rancisco.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66536f1c20abc1efe8fdc3b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFile%20image%2C%20an%20artist%20rendering%20showing%20Ross%20Ulbricht%20during%20an%20appearance%20at%20Federal%20Court%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FVicki%20Behringer%2C%20File%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20vowed%20to%20commute%20Ross%20Ulbricht's%20sentence%20at%20the%20Libertarian%20National%20Convention.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELibertarians%20view%20Ulbricht's%20life%20sentence%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20government%20overreach.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20also%20promised%20to%20include%20a%20Libertarian%20in%20his%20cabinet%20if%20elected.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20made%20an%20address%20at%20the%20Libertarian%20National%20Convention%20on%20Saturday%2C%20promising%20to%20commute%20the%20sentence%20of%20Ross%20Ulbricht%2C%20the%20jailed%20founder%20of%20the%20infamous%20online%20drug%20marketplace%20Silk%20Road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20vote%20for%20me%2C%20on%20Day%20One%2C%20I%20will%20commute%20the%20sentence%20of%20Ross%20Ulbricht%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20declared%20to%20enthusiastic%20applause%20from%20the%20crowd%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20highlight%20Ulbricht%20was%20strategically%20catered%20to%20Libertarian%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUlbricht%2C%20now%2040%2C%20who%20was%20imprisoned%20for%20life%20in%202015%2C%20is%20an%20unjustly%20imprisoned%20hero%20of%20the%20US%20libertarian%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Libertarian%20Party%2C%20with%20its%20long-standing%20advocacy%20for%20drug%20legalization%20and%20criminal%20justice%20reform%2C%20has%20consistently%20lobbied%20for%20Ulbricht's%20release%2C%20viewing%20his%20life%20sentence%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20government%20overreach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUlbricht%20became%20interested%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2F2015%2F04%2Fsilk-road-1%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elibertarian%20values%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20university%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Wired%20report%2C%20where%20he%20discovered%20the%20ideas%20of%20Austrian%20economist%20Ludwig%20von%20Mises%2C%20an%20advocate%20of%20the%20moral%20purpose%20of%20free-market%20capitalism%20and%20staunch%20opponent%20of%20interventionism.%20Ulbricht%20embraced%20these%20ideas%20of%20uncompromised%20freedom%2C%20per%20Wired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20created%20Silk%20Road%2C%20I%20wasn't%20seeking%20financial%20gain%2C%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconvicted-silk-road-mastermind-please-leave-me-my-old-age-2015-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Ulbricht's%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F2086668-gov-uscourts-nysd-422824-251-1.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewrote%20in%20a%20heartfelt%20letter%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20his%20trial%20judge%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20created%20Silk%20Road%20because%20I%20believed%20at%20the%20time%20that%20people%20should%20have%20the%20right%20to%20buy%20and%20sell%20whatever%20they%20wanted%20so%20long%20as%20they%20weren't%20hurting%20anyone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20he%20was%20given%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdny%2Fpr%2Fross-ulbricht-aka-dread-pirate-roberts-sentenced-manhattan-federal-court-life-prison%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20life%20in%20prison%20without%20the%20possibility%20of%20parole%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20also%20fined%20%24183%2C961%2C921.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUlbricht%20is%20being%20held%20at%20the%20United%20States%20Penitentiary%20in%20Tucson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20goods%20sold%20on%20Silk%20Road%20were%20illegal%20hardcore%20drugs%2C%20said%20the%20United%20States%20Attorney's%20Office%20for%20the%20Southern%20District%20of%20New%20York%20at%20his%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSilk%20Road%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20about%20giving%20people%20the%20freedom%20to%20make%20their%20own%20choices%2C%20to%20pursue%20their%20own%20happiness%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Ulbricht.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20still%20don't%20think%20people%20should%20be%20denied%20this%20right%2C%20I%20never%20sought%20to%20create%20a%20site%20that%20would%20provide%20another%20avenue%20for%20people%20to%20feed%20their%20addictions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Members%20of%20the%20Libertarian%20Party%20stand%20in%20chairs%20while%20chanting%20and%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20Ross%20Ulbricht%20during%20the%20party's%20national%20convention%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665370f0239fda2da6cbd7e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Libertarian%20Party%20stand%20in%20chairs%20while%20chanting%20and%20demanding%20the%20release%20of%20Ross%20Ulbricht%20during%20the%20party's%20national%20convention%20at%20the%20Washington%20Hilton%20on%20May%2025%2C%202024%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20was%20loudly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-confronted-with-loud-boos-and-heckles-at-libertarian-convention-2024-5%3Fmrfhud%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebooed%20and%20heckled%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20much%20of%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20Libertarian%20National%20Convention%2C%20did%20manage%20to%20partially%20win%20the%20audience%20around%20by%20committing%20to%20free%20Ulbricht.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Yeniscavich%2C%20a%20Libertarian%20Party%20national%20committee%20member%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F05%2F25%2Ftrump-commute-ross-ulbricht-sentence-libertarian-convention-