n%20for%20the%20last%2010%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20friends%20called%20and%20told%20me%20that%20there%20was%20a%20blast%20at%20the%20childcare%20hospital%20in%20Delhi%20where%20my%20daughter%20was.%20When%20I%20found%20out%20and%20came%20here%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20my%20daughter%20had%20passed%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20three%20families%20among%20the%20six%20of%20them%20have%20lost%20children%20before%20and%20are%20reliving%20the%20ordeal%20after%20their%20newborn%20babies%20died%20in%20the%20fire.%20Masialam%2C%20a%20labourer%20and%20a%20father%20of%20one%20of%20the%20fire%20victims%20had%20lost%20a%20son%20five%20years%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20lost%20my%20newborn%20son.%20What%20kind%20of%20facilities%20do%20they%20have%3F%20You%20can%20ask%20the%20parents%20who%20have%20sold%20their%20jewellery%20or%20took%20money%20on%20interest%20for%20the%20treatment%20of%20their%20kids.%20I%20am%20a%20labourer%20and%20after%20finding%20out%20that%20the%20child%2C%20who%20was%20born%20in%20Manglam%20Hospital%2C%20had%20an%20infection%2C%20we%20admitted%20him%20to%20this%20hospital.%20I%20have%20a%20three-year-old%20daughter%20and%20lost%20a%20son%20around%20five%20years%20back.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParvinder%20Kumar%2C%20the%20relative%20of%20another%20fire%20victim%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20not%20even%20informed%20the%20mother%20yet.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20the%20first%20child%20of%20my%20relative%2C%20Pawan%20Kumar.%20We%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20the%20incident%20unfolded.%20The%20girl%20was%20born%20around%20six%20days%20ago%20at%20a%20hospital%20in%20Ghaziabad%20and%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20care%20centre%20the%20same%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20having%20breathing%20issues%20when%20she%20was%20born%20and%20was%20showing%20improvement%20in%20the%20care%20centre.%20Our%20relative%20called%20us%20around%209%20am%20and%20informed%20us%20about%20the%20incident.%20The%20negligence%20was%20on%20the%20hospital's%20part.%20Strict%20action%20must%20be%20taken%20against%20its%20owner%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parvinder%20said.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20stated%20that%20they%20are%20farmers%20and%20belong%20to%20the%20Baghpat%20district%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Hritik%20Chaudhary%2C%20whose%20newborn%20son%20also%20died%20in%20the%20fire%2C%20said%20that%20every%20single%20official%20who%20is%20visiting%20the%20hospital%20is%20tight-lipped.%20They%20have%20no%20answer%20if%20the%20hospital%20was%20legal%2C%20or%20whether%20the%20hospital%20had%20an%20NOC%20from%20the%20fire%20department.%C2%A0%20Chaudhary's%20cousin%2C%20Robin%20said%20that%20nobody%20informed%20them%20about%20the%20incident%20and%20they%20came%20to%20the%20spot%20after%20watching%20the%20news.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20confusion%20and%20lack%20of%20information%20left%20many%20families%20in%20despair%20when%20they%20reached%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%20After%20the%20incident%2C%20District%20Magistrate%20(DM)%2C%20Shahdara%2C%20Ritisha%20Gupta%20also%20reached%20the%20GTB%20Hospital.%20Many%20families%20stood%20outside%20and%20raised%20slogans%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EHumein%20Insaaf%20Chahiye%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(we%20want%20justice)%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716739500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fnvifiq0g_hospital-fire-1200_625x300_26_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffamilies-struggling-to-identify-their-newborn-babies-killed-in-delhi-hospital-fire-5750819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20devastating%20fire%20that%20killed%20seven%20newborn%20babies%20at%20a%20Delhi%20childcare%20hospital%2C%2