ny-shared-netanyahus-son-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716739338000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66533a5f20abc1efe8fdc09f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-alleged-idf-soldier-threatening-gaza-mutiny-shared-netanyahus-son-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BReservist%20soldiers%20do%20not%20intend%20to%20hand%20the%20keys%20over%20to%20any%20Palestinian%20authority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20alleged%20reservist%20said%20in%20the%20video%2C%20per%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-alleged-idf-soldier-threatening-gaza-mutiny-shared-netanyahus-son-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doctor%20On%20Duty%20Not%20Qualified%20To%20Treat%20Babies%3A%20Delhi%20Police%20On%20Hospital%20Fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExpired%20licence%2C%20doctor%20on%20duty%20not%20qualified%20to%20treat%20newborns%2C%20no%20emergency%20exits%20-%20these%20are%20among%20several%20lapses%20that%20have%20surfaced%20after%20a%20massive%20blaze%20at%20a%20children's%20hospital%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20that%20killed%20seven%20newborn%20babies.%20The%20police%20evacuated%20twelve%20infants%20from%20the%20building%20after%20receiving%20a%20call%20about%20the%20massive%20fire%20at%20Baby%20Care%20New%20Born%20Hospital%20in%20east%20Delhi's%20Vivek%20Vihar%20at%2011.29%20pm%20on%20Saturday.%20Of%20these%2C%20five%20survived%20the%20accident%20and%20were%20shifted%20to%20another%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20fire%20-%20which%20had%20quickly%20spread%20to%20two%20adjacent%20buildings%20-%20was%20doused%2C%20the%20hospital%20was%20thoroughly%20inspected%20by%20police%2C%20fire%20brigade%20staff%20and%20a%20crime%20team.%20The%20teams%20found%20out%20that%20after%20the%20fire%20broke%20out%2C%20oxygen%20cylinders%20kept%20in%20the%20two-storey%20building%20exploded%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20adjacent%20buildings%20were%20damaged.%20What%20also%20came%20to%20light%20were%20several%20shortcomings%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20hospital%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Fire%20Extinguishers%20Or%20Emergency%20Exit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20inspection%20of%20the%20hospital%20and%20examination%20of%20nursing%20staff%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20the%20facility%20didn't%20have%20any%20fire%20extinguishers%20or%20an%20emergency%20exit%2C%20police%20said.%20The%20doctor%20who%20was%20on%20duty%20when%20the%20accident%20happened%20was%20not%20qualified%20to%20treat%20newborns%20in%20need%20of%20neo-natal%20incentive%20care%2C%20they%20added.%20Dr%20Akash%20-%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Ayurvedic%20Medicine%20and%20Surgery%20(BAMS)%20graduate%20-%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Shahdara)%20Surendra%20Chaudhary%20said%20that%20the%20hospital%20had%20more%20than%20the%20authorised%20number%20of%20oxygen%20cylinders.%20%26quot%3BInitially%2C%20we%20had%20filed%20a%20case%20for%20negligence.%20After%20the%20inspection%2C%20we%20have%20also%20invoked%20sections%20304%20(culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder)%20and%20308%20(attempt%20to%20commit%20culpable%20homicide)%20of%20IPC%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpired%20Licence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20licence%20issued%20to%20the%20hospital%20by%20the%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Health%20Services%20or%20DGHS%20had%20already%20expired%20on%20March%2031%2C%20nearly%20two%20months%20before%20the%20accident.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20police%20said%20even%20though%20the%20licence%20allowed%20for%20five%20beds%20at%20the%20facility%2C%20twelve%20newborns%20were%20in%20the%20hospital%20when%20the%20fire%20broke%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20probe%20into%20the%20accident%20disclosed%20that%20the%20hospital%20has%20three%20other%20branches%20in%20Punjabi%20Bagh%20(Delhi)%2C%20Faridabad%20(Haryana)%20and%20Gurgaon%20(Haryana).%20Dr%20Naveen%20Khichi%2C%20a%20Doctor%20of%20Medicine%20(MD)%20in%20Pediatrics%2C%20is%20the%20owner%20of%20these%20branches.%20Dr%20Khichi%20and%20his%20wife%20Dr%20Jagriti%2C%20a%20dentist%2C%20run%20the%20Vivek%20Vihar%20facility%2C%20the%20police%20said.%20The%20owner%20(45)%2C%20who%20had%20been%20on%20the%20run%20since%20Saturday%20night%2C%20has%20also%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20announced%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20from%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20National%20Relief%20Fund%20(PMNRF)%20for%20the%20families%20of%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20has%20ordered%20a%20magisterial%20inquiry%20into%20the%20fire%20tragedy%20at%20the%20neonatal%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716738780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F3l3lak3g_delhi-hospital-fire-pti_625x300_26_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-childrens-hospital-fire-expired-licence-no-fire-extinguishers-lapses-surface-after-hospital-blaze-5751199%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Expired%20licence%2C%20doctor%20on%20duty%20not%20qualified%20to%20treat%20newborns%2C%20no%20emergency%20exits%20-%20these%20are%20among%20several%20lapses%20that%20have%20surfaced%20after%20a%20massive%20blaze%20at%20a%20children's%20hospital%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20that%20killed%20seven%20newborn%20babies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-childrens-hospital-fire-expired-licence-no-fire-extinguishers-lapses-surface-after-hospital-blaze-5751199%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-childrens-hospital-fire-