nt%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20hamburgers%20have%20garnered%20a%20reputation%20for%20their%20longevity%2C%20but%20none%20have%20achieved%20the%20notoriety%20of%20a%20seemingly%20unaltered%20Quarter%20Pounder%20from%20Australia.%20This%20particular%20burger%2C%20purchased%20nearly%20three%20decades%20ago%2C%20exhibits%20no%20signs%20of%20decomposition%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F05%2F24%2Flifestyle%2Fmcdonalds-burger-from-1995-still-perfectly-intact-even-rats-wont-eat-it%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20documented%20claim%2C%20Casey%20Dean%20and%20Eduards%20Nits%2C%20two%20Australian%20residents%2C%20purchased%20the%20Quarter%20Pounder%20with%20cheese%20in%201995%20from%20a%20McDonald's%20location%20in%20Adelaide.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20Bill%20Clinton%20served%20as%20the%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20Little%20did%20they%20know%2C%20this%20seemingly%20ordinary%20purchase%20would%20propel%20the%20burger%20into%20the%20realm%20of%20fast-food%20legend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20teenagers%20we%20ordered%20a%20truckload%20of%20food%2C%20and%20it%20was%20just%20way%20too%20much%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dean%20told%20%3Cem%3EAFP%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt%20started%20a%20chain%20of%20events%20where%20we%20were%20joking%20'imagine%20if%20we%20kept%20this%20forever.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20their%20initial%20purchase%2C%20Dean%20and%20Nits%20opted%20to%20retain%20the%20seemingly%20impervious%20burger%2C%20affectionately%20naming%20it%20%26quot%3Btheir%20mate.%26quot%3B%20Nearly%20three%20decades%20later%2C%20the%20remarkably%20well-preserved%20burger%2C%20now%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3BMcFossil%2C%26quot%3B%20exhibits%20no%20signs%20of%20microbial%20growth%20or%20discernible%20odour.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20undergone%20a%20slight%20reduction%20in%20size%20compared%20to%20its%20original%20dimensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20McFossil's%20longevity%20is%20particularly%20noteworthy%20given%20its%20storage%20environment.%20The%20majority%20of%20its%20existence%20has%20been%20spent%20within%20a%20basic%20cardboard%20and%20wooden%20container.%20Notably%2C%20it%20endured%20over%20a%20decade%20in%20a%20warm%20Adelaide%20shed%2C%20where%20summer%20temperatures%20routinely%20surpass%2030%20degrees%20Celsius%20(86%20degrees%20Fahrenheit).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rats%20had%20actually%20eaten%20through%20the%20plastic%20bag%2C%20heaps%20of%20clothes%2C%20got%20into%20the%20box%20and%20they'd%20left%20the%20burger%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubbing%20it%20the%20%26quot%3BSenior%20Burger%26quot%3B%20and%20referring%20to%20it%20repeatedly%20as%20their%20%26quot%3Bmate%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20men%20have%20created%20social%20media%20profiles%20for%20the%20burger%20and%20even%20wrote%20a%20song%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20believe%20it%20is%20the%20oldest%20known%20McDonald's%20burger%20in%20the%20world%2C%20outranking%20a%20prominent%20decade-old%20cheeseburger%20displayed%20in%20a%20glass%20case%20in%20Iceland%20and%20live-streamed%20online%20to%20thousands%20of%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStorage%20for%20the%20ancient%20Aussie%20burger%20has%20been%20rather%20less%20considered%2C%20though%20it%20has%20mostly%20been%20kept%20under%20lock%20and%20key%20in%20a%20box%20made%20of%20timber%20and%20cardboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20box%20spent%20about%20a%20decade%20jumbled%20up%20with%20clothing%20inside%20a%20shed%20in%20Adelaide%2C%20where%20temperatures%20regularly%20top%2030%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20eventually%20went%20to%20check%20on%20it%2C%20Dean%20said%20even%20rats%20had%20turned%20their%20noses%20up%20at%20the%20morsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rats%20had%20actually%20eaten%20through%20the%20plastic%20bag%2C%20heaps%20of%20clothes%2C%20got%20into%20the%20box%20and%20they'd%20left%20the%20burger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20mate%20was%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDean%20said%20he%20understood%20why%20some%20might%20be%20sceptical%20about%20their%20claim%2C%20but%20argues%20the%20old-school%20packaging%20--%20waxy%20paper%20and%20a%20cardboard%20ring%20--%20accurately%20dates%20the%20burger%20to%20the%20mid-1990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20steadfast%20that%20the%20pair%20would%20never%20part%20with%20it%20despite%20fielding%20offers%20from%20around%20the%20world%20when%20it%20first%20came%20to%20public%20attention%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716730980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fftupjhj_mcfossil_625x300_26_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fthis-mcdonalds-burger-bought-in-1995-is-still-perfectly-intact-5750593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Casey%20Dean%20and%20Eduards%20Nits%2C%20two%20Australian%20residents%2C%20purchased%20the%20Quarter%20Pounder%20with%20cheese%20in%201995%20from%20a%20McDonald's%20location%20in%20Adelaide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fthis-mcdonalds-burger-bought-in-1995-is-still-perfectly-intact-5750593%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fthis-mcdonalds-burger-bought-in-1995-is-still-perfectly-intact-5750593%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fthis-mcdonalds-burger-bought-in-1995-is-still-perfectly-intact-5750593%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Huge%20160mph%20crash%20at%20Monaco%20Grand%20Prix%20halts%20F1%20race%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716730560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F05%2F1920x1080%2Fsky-sports-pere-perez-magunsson_6566431.jpg%3F20240526163623%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhuge-160mph-crash-at-monaco-grand-pr