g%20back.%20Saravanan%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%2C%20shares%20that%20he%20has%20been%20eating%20at%20Dhanam%20%3Cem%3EPaati%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20shop%20since%20he%20was%20a%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20taste%20of%20her%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20coconut%20chutney%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekurma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mixed%20vegetable%20gravy)%20is%20unparalleled.%20If%20we%20ask%20for%20three%20idlis%2C%20she%20will%20always%20give%20two%20extra%20without%20charging%20for%20it.%20If%20one%20is%20short%20of%20money%2C%20she%20waives%20it%20off.%20All%20she%20wants%20is%20that%20we%20leave%20feeling%20full%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Help%20me%20build%20a%20permanent%20house%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20might%20also%20wonder%20why%20she%20continues%20to%20work%20well%20into%20her%2080s.%20Her%20son%20and%20daughter%20are%20struggling%20too%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20which%20is%20why%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20burden%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201345px)%20100vw%2C%201345px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221345%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dhanam%20Paati's%20house%20is%20in%20dire%20straits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333.jpeg%201345w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333-300x201.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333-500x335.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333-768x515.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fdhanam3-min-min-1716293333-150x101.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2